---

<Layout
  title="Speaking | Vaughn Cyber Group"
  description="Cybersecurity keynotes and executive sessions by Lora Vaughn. Book her to speak at your event."
  image="/images/headshot-square.png"
  url="https://vaughncybergroup.com/speaking"
>
<main class="flex flex-col gap-y-20 md:gap-y-32 overflow-hidden">
 <section class="relative pt-20 lg:pt-24 bg-[rgb(var(--color-bg))] text-[rgb(var(--heading-1))]">
  <!-- Reduced vertical gap between text and potential image/content columns -->
  <Container className={"flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6 lg:gap-8"}>

    <!-- Gradient Background Blobs -->
    <div class="absolute w-full lg:w-1/2 inset-y-0 lg:right-0">
      <span class="absolute -left-6 md:left-4 top-24 lg:top-28 w-24 h-24 rotate-90 skew-x-12 rounded-3xl bg-[rgb(var(--color-teal))] blur-xl opacity-60 lg:opacity-95 hidden lg:block"></span>
      <span class="absolute right-4 bottom-12 w-24 h-24 rounded-3xl bg-[rgb(var(--color-pink))] blur-xl opacity-80"></span>
    </div>

    <!-- Large Gradient Accent -->
    <span class="w-4/12 lg:w-2/12 aspect-square bg-gradient-to-tr from-[rgb(var(--color-pink))] to-[rgb(var(--color-teal))] absolute -top-5 lg:left-0 rounded-full skew-y-12 blur-2xl opacity-40 skew-x-12 rotate-90"></span>

    <!-- Text Column -->
    <!-- Reduced vertical padding to eliminate bottom gap inside text section -->
    <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center text-center lg:text-left py-0 lg:py-2 
                lg:items-start lg:max-w-none max-w-3xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 lg:flex-1 lg:w-1/2">

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-bold text-[rgb(var(--heading-1))]">
         
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br 
          from-[rgb(var(--gradient-start))] 
          via-[rgb(var(--gradient-mid))] 
          to-[rgb(var(--gradient-end))]">

      Cybersecurity That Connects</h1>
      <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold mb-4 text-heading-1">
        Speaking, Keynotes & Cybersecurity Education by Lora Vaughn
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-heading-2 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        From boardrooms to global conferences, Lora delivers high-impact talks that blend strategic insight, real-world security leadership, and a deep commitment to building resilient organizations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Headshot Section -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-box">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col items-center text-center px-6">
      <img src="/images/headshot-square.png" alt="Lora Vaughn headshot"
        class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full object-cover shadow-md mb-6" />
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-heading-1">Meet Lora Vaughn</h2>
      <p class="max-w-lg text-heading-2">
        Lora is an award-winning cybersecurity executive, educator, and speaker. Her talks blend real‑world insight with empathy‑driven leadership, helping organizations build trust, resilience, and security maturity.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Signature Topics Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-bg-base">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-center font-semibold mb-6 text-heading-1">Signature Topics</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-6 text-left text-heading-2">
        <li><strong>Plan for Chaos:</strong> How Incident Response Plans Fail Big</li>
        <li><strong>Measuring Cybersecurity Success:</strong>Crafting Metrics with NIST CSF and Beyond</li>
        <li><strong>Executive Cybersecurity:</strong> What Every Founder and Board Should Know</li>
        <li><strong>Unveiling the Spy in Your Pocket:</strong> How Everyday Apps Are Tracking You — and What You Can Do About It</li>
        <li><strong>Empathy-Driven Security:</strong> The Hidden Superpower of High-Performing Teams</li>
        <li><strong>Should I Stay or Should I Go?</strong> Navigating Career Crossroads in Cybersecurity</li>
        <li><strong>Rethinking Vulnerability Management:</strong> Escaping the Broken CVSS Model</li>

      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Media Examples Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-box">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-8 text-center text-heading-1">Media & Teaching Highlights</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        {examples.map((item) => (
          <article class="p-6 bg-bg-base rounded-lg shadow border border-box">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2 text-heading-2">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm mb-2 text-heading-3">{item.date}</p>
            <p class="text-sm mb-4 text-heading-2">{item.description}</p>
            {item.link && (
              <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-button hover:underline">
                More &rarr;
              </a>
            )}
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Booking CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-bg-base">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-heading-1">Book Lora to Speak</h2>
      <p class="text-md mb-6 text-heading-2">
        Whether you're planning a keynote, panel, or executive briefing—Lora brings clarity and impact to every stage.
      </p>
      <!-- Submit Button -->
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-md sm:max-w-xl pt-10">
          <a href="/contactus">
          <Button variant={"primary"}>
            <span class="text-white relative z-[5]">Request Availability</span>
          </Button>
        </a>
        </div>
      
    </div>
  </section>
</main> 
</Layout>
